31/03/2004
TIRANA, Albania -- Foreign Minister Kastriot Islami spoke by phone with US Undersecretary of State for Political Affairs Marc Grossman, the foreign ministry announced Tuesday (30 March). 
The two discussed the situation in Kosovo. 
Grossman said his recent visit there confirmed the US commitment to stability in Kosovo and the whole region. 
According to the ministry, Islami and Grossman agreed that the solution to the Kosovo issue should be found in multiethnic cohabitation, respect for human rights and the implementation of set standards. 
(ATA - 30/03/04)
